WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.893
Well, good morning family.

00:00:01.893 --> 00:00:03.200
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:06.560
It has been an amazing 24 hours.

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:10.880
I am just burning with the fire of the Lord today.

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:19.651
I am so excited to come on here and talk to you and tell you what the Lord did last night.

00:00:19.651 --> 00:00:27.803
I am in awe at what the Lord—I have so many different directions I could go right now.

00:00:27.803 --> 00:00:40.480
But first, I want to tell you all how exciting it is that I heard all the testimonies about the Coachella assassination attempt.

00:00:41.480 --> 00:00:54.480
The sheriff came on there and said he had fake passports, he had fake driver's license plates, he had guns and everything inside of his car.

00:00:54.766 --> 00:01:01.634
They released him on bail for $5,000, but he didn't do anything because God intervened.

00:01:02.388 --> 00:01:05.233
People were like, "Well, where did you prophesy this?

00:01:05.789 --> 00:01:06.600
"—the doubters.

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:09.794
The Lord had me pray very hard for Coachella.

00:01:09.794 --> 00:01:14.960
I kept praying for this word "Coachella," and I kept getting this in the spirit realm.

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:17.511
So, I told my friend about it and he helped me Google it.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.680
Then my wife helped me Google this word.

00:01:19.980 --> 00:01:25.966
We're going to pray for these major events and big gatherings of people, for nothing to happen.

00:01:25.966 --> 00:01:30.308
The Lord said, "This is how they're going to run their campaign in 2024.

00:01:30.308 --> 00:01:46.106
" And he said, "You need to tell the people to pray and hear the voice of the Lord concerning every place they go in their day-to-day activity, major events, and going with crowds and concerts.

00:01:46.106 --> 00:01:49.874
" That's why I prayed for Coachella.

00:01:49.874 --> 00:01:51.863
The Lord had me praying for this.

00:01:51.863 --> 00:01:54.651
We'll pray against it for this year.

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:59.080
I've been praying over Coachella; there are a lot of events to pray over.

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:08.730
When I warned you all about the shootings at Coachella that were coming up in a couple of days, that was a warning I got this time last year.

00:02:08.730 --> 00:02:11.440
And the Lord told me, "Pray over this.

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:13.340
This is a plot from the enemy.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:17.040
" I told you about George Soros and these people over there.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:30.027
I saw bad men over in Europe having a meeting with the devil at the same time last year when he warned me to pray over Coachella and said that they were plotting something against it.

00:02:38.503 --> 00:02:38.767
The Lord warned me about that and told me to pray for that.

00:02:39.823 --> 00:02:41.679
I intercede for a lot of things, y'all.

00:02:41.679 --> 00:02:45.472
But they said, "Well, you've missed it.

00:02:45.472 --> 00:02:51.680
How many things have you gotten to come to pass that the Lord shows you?

00:02:54.284 --> 00:02:59.200
" And I say, "Man, I've sat on stuff for five years, sometimes longer, before anything ever starts to be in the news.

00:03:04.937 --> 00:03:13.314
" I'm still praying over the thing in Italy the Lord showed me when I warned you all that a major volcano was going to go off and it was going to wipe out the whole coastal city.

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:20.538
I saw over 300,000 people—boom—dead that fast because of the volcano going off.

00:03:20.538 --> 00:03:26.288
I'm trying to steer you all to show you where I'm at and where I've been praying.

00:03:26.288 --> 00:03:32.738
So, praying over Coachella, and then the Lord was warning me about big gatherings again.

00:03:33.751 --> 00:03:42.346
I was sent an email and even a text from a friend telling me, "Hey, do you remember praying over Coachella?

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:48.529
" I got this and I've been praying over Coachella.

00:03:48.899 --> 00:04:00.479
The Lord will show me, like I said, way in advance of events trying to manifest, and I take authority over them so that they don't manifest.

00:04:00.799 --> 00:04:07.783
I saw a mass shooting event happening at Coachella and the Lord said, "I want you to pray over this event so that this does not take place.

00:04:13.943 --> 00:04:14.331
" Well, I thought it was the concert event.

00:04:14.331 --> 00:04:16.400
Maybe it was; I don't know.

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:27.680
Like I said, we hear in part and we see in part.

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:36.062
So when you're looking through the filter of what the Lord is trying to tell you, you just keep praying.

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.337
The Lord told me to start praying over this, that this was a serious thing to pray over.

00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:51.177
Well, my friend sent me a text and he said, "Hey Brandon, did you see that President Trump was going to Coachella to hold a rally there?

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:55.360
" I had no idea.

00:04:59.947 --> 00:05:06.720
So, with the things that you get in the spirit of warnings and prayer, you try to put your own mind to it and you get in trouble because you're thinking it's the concert.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.503
All I know is that's what we pray.

00:05:08.503 --> 00:05:25.280
Whether it was the presidential thing that's going to happen this weekend with the speech and all that, I don't know, because all I know is the Lord warned me and told me to pray over this stuff.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:32.274
But did it witness with me that this could be it?

00:05:32.274 --> 00:05:33.200
Yeah.

00:05:43.189 --> 00:05:43.440
I thought this is probably it.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:06:03.253
More than likely, we were going to pray over Coachella again, this Trump rally that's coming on Saturday, and if there are any plots or any plans, we call them exposed in Jesus' name—that they would be caught in the name of Jesus.

00:06:03.253 --> 00:06:12.020
We call for supernatural wisdom over the Secret Service, supernatural wisdom over the FBI—the good FBI—CIA, Homeland Security, all of them.

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:22.027
The Riverside County Sheriff's Department just announced an arrest from former President Donald Trump's rally in Coachella.

00:06:22.027 --> 00:06:32.914
If you're asking me right now, I probably did have deputies that prevented the third assassination attempt.

00:06:32.914 --> 00:06:42.720
A man carrying several guns and fake passes was stopped by police at a rally in Coachella Valley over the weekend.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:55.520
This is not about boasting about my platform, but about warning you to pray and intercede on behalf of America because God is not done with America.

00:06:55.520 --> 00:07:00.777
God is not finished with what he's about to do in America.

00:07:00.777 --> 00:07:09.017
There is going to be a great harvest of souls beyond anybody's comprehension that's about to come to this land.

00:07:09.017 --> 00:07:17.866
I was thinking about the old Welsh revival and how they said the glory of God came with fire.

00:07:17.866 --> 00:07:36.570
It happened so strongly that the miners who would work in the mines in Wales in that area had to shut down the mines because the mules and the donkeys that were working only knew how to take commands with cuss words.

00:07:36.570 --> 00:07:51.744
But when the fire of God came on those miners and they got the Holy Ghost on their mouths and were delivered from things, they stopped the profanity.

00:08:03.783 --> 00:08:04.160
So, the donkeys and the mules did not know how to respond anymore.

00:08:04.686 --> 00:08:07.920
They had to shut down the mines because the glory came.

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:11.120
It took time to train the donkeys and the mules again.

00:08:16.060 --> 00:08:17.989
The glory came there, and they were asking one little girl, "What do you feel about what's happened to the revival here?

00:08:28.299 --> 00:08:28.489
" And she said, "It's like Jesus; we have Sunday every day.

00:08:28.489 --> 00:08:35.462
" All I can say is, "Lord, do it again.

00:08:35.462 --> 00:08:42.436
" There was an awe with the presence of God throughout the whole city.

00:08:42.436 --> 00:08:46.640
There was an awe on every street corner.

00:08:57.417 --> 00:08:57.680
And I'm telling you, we had revivals in the 1700s with John Wesley and Finney.

00:09:01.929 --> 00:09:11.600
The glory would come so strongly when they would preach in these revivals that they would tell people to get out of the trees because they would climb them to get a better view.

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:45.653
But John Wesley would warn them to get out of the trees because when he would speak, the glory of God would fill up the outside—not in an inside building—but the presence of the Lord would weigh so strongly that the power of God would knock people out of the trees, and he didn't want them to get hurt.

00:09:45.653 --> 00:09:49.040
I'm telling you, a glory will come again.

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:52.960
I'm telling you, an outpouring of his presence is coming again.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:10:00.880
One last call: the Lord warns me and tells me today when I pray.

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:06.510
Thank God he spared Trump's life again.

00:10:06.510 --> 00:10:12.840
It was a call to prayer for 30 days.

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:16.680
But the enemy has a plan, ladies and gentlemen.

00:10:25.874 --> 00:10:35.650
I've told you even five or six days after the election—if you didn't believe me before, do you believe me now when I tell you the Lord tells me to come on here and warn you about what's coming?

00:10:35.650 --> 00:10:42.308
Maybe this time when you see the next sign, maybe you will listen.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:59.028
I pray you do because I'm trying as a watchman on the wall, yelling with all I have to warn you that Jesus Christ is coming—not for anything else, but to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:10:59.028 --> 00:11:07.719
Jesus is coming, and there is a great outpouring of His Spirit that's coming.

00:11:07.719 --> 00:11:11.620
There is a great shaking to awaken.

00:11:11.620 --> 00:11:17.419
People don't want to hear about the other side of the coin, the dark side.

00:11:17.419 --> 00:11:21.645
But there are dark days coming, just as there are light days coming.

00:11:35.210 --> 00:11:35.560
I try very hard now to speak about both.

00:11:41.449 --> 00:11:59.009
But when I have told you about financial crisis, things that I've seen coming—a dollar shaking, worth fifty cents on the dollar, the seizing of the monies in the bank, warning you of a Great Depression with people lined up for miles trying to get food—warning you that I've seen an asteroid hit in the Atlantic Ocean, a great explosion in Poland, and an acceleration of war.

00:11:59.009 --> 00:12:12.789
I've seen Israel attack Iran and the oil, so much so that Saudi Arabia and the BRICS nations will come together stronger against the petrodollar.

00:12:12.789 --> 00:12:19.520
I saw the oil go over two hundred dollars a barrel.

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:27.360
I saw gasoline going well over eight, nine, or ten dollars a gallon on average.

00:12:29.497 --> 00:12:29.874
Is it supposed to scare you?

00:12:33.790 --> 00:12:34.040
No.

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:37.280
It's to warn you and to prepare you.

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:49.227
I bring these things up to warn you, to shake you, to say, 'Listen, we can pray.

00:12:49.227 --> 00:13:11.800
' I didn't come on this channel to tickle your ears or to entertain you, to make you go, 'Well, that was a really good message; it gave me goosebumps,' and then go back to your apathy, your laziness, and your being slothful and asleep.

00:13:11.800 --> 00:13:17.672
I come on here to shake you, to tell you that there's a plan afoot for the devil's work.

00:13:17.672 --> 00:13:20.223
But God has a plan that's bigger.

00:13:22.336 --> 00:13:42.386
And if we would plug ourselves in and get excited about what God is going to do in these last days, and humble ourselves and pray and turn from our wicked ways, then He said we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.

00:13:43.991 --> 00:13:46.251
You all think Donald Trump is going to save America.

00:13:46.251 --> 00:13:54.776
But there is only one person that will save America, and that is Jesus Christ and an awakening unto God.

00:13:54.776 --> 00:14:00.799
America will not be saved without an awakening unto God.

00:14:00.799 --> 00:14:09.540
America is in the place where we're trying to change the fruit of America without changing the root.

00:14:40.684 --> 00:14:41.067
And a lot of you think we can just change the fruit, but the problem is the root is bad.

00:14:41.067 --> 00:14:45.746
Donald Trump isn't going to change the fruit.

00:15:04.044 --> 00:15:04.347
The problem is we're not preaching righteousness and holiness in the pulpits anymore.

00:15:04.347 --> 00:15:06.914
We preach a lukewarm, seeker-friendly message.

00:15:06.914 --> 00:16:02.693
We're feeding the babies porridge and milk, and they don't have meat to grow because we aren't teaching the Word of God to the people—the meat of the Word, the ABCs of faith—teaching them how to live by faith and how to stay strong, how to cast out devils, to do the Great Commission, to lay hands on the sick and see them recover, to raise the dead, to bring sight to the blind, to open ears, and to tell the lame to leap and walk.

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:08.374
We have that ability on the inside of us.

00:16:08.374 --> 00:16:21.822
Jesus Christ lives on the inside of every single one of you.

00:16:22.711 --> 00:16:27.279
And I have such an urgency today, an urgency to tell you like Paul Revere yelling on his horse, 'The British are coming!

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:28.719
The British are coming!

00:16:28.719 --> 00:16:44.186
' but to tell you in the midnight hour that I'm riding on the horse through town after town via this YouTube channel, telling the whole world that Jesus Christ is coming, and yet you're still asleep.

00:16:49.849 --> 00:16:50.098
I yell from the mountaintops that Jesus is coming.

00:16:50.844 --> 00:16:52.579
I had a visitation again last night.

00:16:52.579 --> 00:17:13.259
I cannot tell you what He said this time because it was for me, but I can tell you this: He said, 'A lot of the older generals are going to start to go home, and you're going to see a new generation of Davids rise up.

00:17:13.259 --> 00:17:19.332
' You will see this shortly: a great move of His presence beyond anything you've ever seen before.

00:17:19.332 --> 00:17:24.519
It's not years away anymore; it's not days away.

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:40.249
It's now.

00:17:40.249 --> 00:17:43.977
You're going to start to see the manifestation of things.

00:17:43.977 --> 00:17:49.840
I'm telling you all, it's time to get your hearts right before the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:55.920
It's time for you to seek Him like you've never sought Him before.

00:17:55.920 --> 00:18:02.200
Jesus is the healer; He's the same yesterday, today, and forever, and you're about to see it.

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:13.210
I went to a healing service last night, and the power of God knocked me on my rear.

00:18:13.210 --> 00:18:17.093
My wife and children were all touched by the glory.

00:18:17.093 --> 00:18:20.224
And we got a word from the minister there.

00:18:27.060 --> 00:18:27.470
We prayed for my little girl Megan, and the glory filled the room.

00:18:29.933 --> 00:18:38.864
You know, when you go and you're not expecting much, you're just excited to be a part of things.

00:18:38.864 --> 00:18:42.280
I never anticipate anything like that—a word from anybody.

00:18:42.280 --> 00:18:45.173
I just go and want to watch someone else get blessed.

00:18:45.173 --> 00:18:48.240
I'm excited just to be there.

00:18:54.880 --> 00:19:00.907
But he asked for people to come up and tell their testimonies about what God had done for them in the past.

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:16.240
And I went and told them about taking her to that service a couple of years ago when he prayed for her and, within a week or two, my daughter was completely potty trained.

00:19:16.240 --> 00:19:20.560
Supernaturally, even though the doctors said Megan would never be potty trained.

00:19:20.560 --> 00:19:34.831
They told us that she would maintain the level of eighteen months for the rest of her life and to never expect her to be potty trained.

00:19:34.831 --> 00:19:37.904
There were so many negative things that neuropsychologist said.

00:19:37.904 --> 00:19:43.332
That's when I told him all things are possible to him that believes.

00:20:06.816 --> 00:20:07.632
He told my wife, 'You all are in denial.

00:20:07.632 --> 00:20:12.366
You need to come to reality.

00:20:12.366 --> 00:20:25.669
I've never seen, in thousands and thousands of cases over thirty or forty years, an autistic child ever healed.

00:20:25.669 --> 00:20:38.559
' And that's when my wife looked at him and said, 'But my daughter will be.

00:20:38.559 --> 00:20:43.454
She'll be the first, and we're going to come back here and give you a testimony.

00:20:43.454 --> 00:20:48.250
' Well, we stood and stood, and when there is nothing else to do, you stand.

00:20:48.250 --> 00:20:56.879
Whenever you don't see the fruit of what you're believing for in full manifestation, you keep standing.

00:20:58.079 --> 00:21:01.380
You don't give up.

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:06.551
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:21:06.551 --> 00:21:10.583
So we believe some more; we keep standing.

00:21:13.600 --> 00:21:16.480
You find your Bible verses, you keep reading them, and you keep believing it.

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:20.680
Then we had the encounter, and Megan started pottying on the stool.

00:21:20.680 --> 00:21:27.420
Within just a day, she woke up, sat down, and went to the bathroom—that was a miracle in itself, and it's been progressive.

00:21:40.273 --> 00:21:40.868
But a miracle is a miracle even if it's progressive, especially when you realize how far she has come.

00:21:40.868 --> 00:21:51.440
Well, last night we took her again, and he asked if anybody had a testimony.

00:21:51.440 --> 00:22:15.120
So I went down to the front to tell him about Megan, just excited about it, saying, 'God, this is a big deal,' because we spent a lot of money on adult diapers, and they're very expensive.

00:22:15.120 --> 00:22:21.039
He laid hands on her, and the power of God went all over her.

00:22:21.039 --> 00:22:32.160
He gave us a word about our ministry, gave a word over my wife, and really filled us with fire and encouragement.

00:22:32.160 --> 00:22:34.080
I'm expecting a supernatural turnaround.

00:22:34.080 --> 00:22:45.244
I'm expecting—I told you there will be a day when my daughter comes on here and tells you all the goodness of our God, that Jesus is the healer.

00:22:45.244 --> 00:22:55.725
He is a healer, and He is going to visit America one last time in a mighty outpouring of His Spirit.

00:22:55.725 --> 00:23:00.284
Coachella was just a prayer assignment.

00:23:00.284 --> 00:23:07.924
That's the way he deals with me all the time.

00:23:07.924 --> 00:23:27.623
Like I said, the more you get to know me, I come on and do these videos over these 30 days.

00:23:27.623 --> 00:23:35.329
People are asking me to continue to do it afterwards.

00:23:35.329 --> 00:23:37.609
We'll see; I probably will.

00:23:54.524 --> 00:23:54.729
I feel an urgency to do this more and more.

00:23:54.729 --> 00:23:58.444
I just thought you all would get tired of it and not show up.

00:23:58.444 --> 00:24:06.919
I mean, honestly, I thought, 'Well, if the people show up and they want to pray, we might as well pray.

00:24:06.919 --> 00:24:11.013
' You know, whenever people don't show up, it's discouraging.

00:24:16.176 --> 00:24:16.688
You go, 'Well, what's the point?

00:24:16.688 --> 00:24:26.339
' That is what you think in your natural mind.

00:24:26.339 --> 00:24:42.413
If they're not going to show up and pray, then whatever.

00:24:42.413 --> 00:24:45.760
But God had an assignment.

00:24:45.760 --> 00:24:55.510
I didn't know what the turnout was going to be, and I really didn't care.

00:24:55.510 --> 00:24:57.899
He told me to do it.

00:24:57.899 --> 00:25:02.860
He said, 'Do it,' and I said, 'Okay, Lord, I'll do it.

00:25:02.860 --> 00:25:11.159
' And people are showing up and we're making a difference.

00:25:11.159 --> 00:25:15.848
I'm going to pray today for an outpouring, but we have to take communion first.

00:25:15.848 --> 00:25:17.677
Excuse me.

00:25:17.677 --> 00:25:24.640
Father, we thank you for your body.

00:25:26.320 --> 00:25:33.220
We thank you for what you did on that cross 2,000 years ago.

00:25:33.220 --> 00:25:47.533
We thank you that you said, 'By your stripes, I am healed,' from the top of our head to the soles of our feet, Lord.

00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:15.770
We lift up this body before you, God.

00:26:34.994 --> 00:26:35.509
I thank you that you were wounded for our transgressions, you were bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, we are healed.

00:26:35.509 --> 00:26:37.051
Megan's healed.

00:26:37.051 --> 00:26:37.566
Reed is healed.

00:26:37.566 --> 00:26:54.320
I got a call from a lady who broke her ribs, and I lift up her ribs before you in the name of Jesus.

00:26:54.320 --> 00:27:02.445
I thank you, Father, that you're healing her from the top of her head to her feet.

00:27:02.445 --> 00:27:06.613
All her ribs are healed in Jesus' name.

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:13.632
We say supernaturally, put them back together with a creative miracle with no more pain.

00:27:24.364 --> 00:27:24.693
And we say, 'Satan, get your hands off of God's property.

00:27:24.693 --> 00:27:28.359
' This is his child in Jesus' name.

00:27:34.453 --> 00:27:38.680
Father, I thank you, Lord, for the body right now and we lift it up before you and we thank you.

00:27:38.680 --> 00:27:47.989
We thank you, Father, for what you did for us on Calvary.

00:27:47.989 --> 00:27:51.520
We take this body right now in Jesus' name.

00:27:51.520 --> 00:27:54.813
Now Lord, we lift up the blood and we thank you.

00:27:54.813 --> 00:28:04.400
We enter in by the blood of the lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:28:04.400 --> 00:28:09.320
We have authority over the devil.

00:28:10.200 --> 00:28:11.874
I thank you for the blood, Lord.

00:28:11.874 --> 00:28:28.091
We take this blood right now in the name of Jesus, and it washes us of our sins and we enter into your throne room with great boldness today as we pray.

00:28:35.359 --> 00:28:35.759
We take our dominion and authority over this earth because you've given us dominion and authority.

00:28:35.759 --> 00:28:47.115
We thank you, Father, that we are washed in the blood, the cleansing blood of the lamb.

00:28:48.560 --> 00:28:49.760
Thank you, Father, for the blood.

00:28:49.760 --> 00:28:51.859
Thank you for your blood, Lord.

00:28:51.859 --> 00:28:53.839
It never loses its power.

00:28:53.839 --> 00:28:57.840
We lift up the blood, Father, and we thank you.

00:28:57.840 --> 00:29:03.704
We thank you, Father, for the blood that washes us from all our sins.

00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:21.280
Father, you said to make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of you.

00:29:24.309 --> 00:29:25.880
And we take the blood right now in the name of Jesus.

00:29:41.120 --> 00:29:41.550
Now Lord, we enter in boldly to your throne.

